abstract: >
  A standardized approach to generate shared tRNA coordinates for plotting
  and cross-isodecoder comparisons. Converts heterogeneous Sprinzl-style
  labels from R2DT output into a unified coordinate system that preserves
  per-nucleotide sequence order while enabling cross-tRNA visualization
  on a common equal-spaced axis.
